**Note:**  This JSON utilizes the `IMAGES` component as a placeholder for the image carousel.  The actual implementation of this component (and the image URLs) would depend on the specific design system capabilities.  Similarly, seller information and other supporting elements would be added as additional `items` within the main `layoutContainer`, leveraging available components or fallback to native elements.  The `componentNodeId` values are placeholders and should be replaced with actual IDs from the provided `DESIGN_SYSTEM_DATA`.  This example focuses on demonstrating the application of design system intelligence.


